channel.title: Help!
channel.description:
Ik this isnt an error in the compiler, but it says the message that says recompile with xlint. My server wont update i was trying to fix one of the shops, and then i tried to change the name, then i tried to add a pk box, but it all wont work. Everything in the server is the same. I checked it and saved. I go back and all the settings i put in are the same but then when i compile it comes up with that message. I start the server and it works fine, but then i login and none of the changes i made are on there. Any solutions?
Thanks, Lilgdog13
